Write a C program that calculates and prints the sum of all even numbers from 1 to a given positive integer n. Use a while loop to iterate through the numbers.

Sample 1:
Input           Output
6                 12


#include <stdio.h>
int main(void) {
	int n, sum = 0, i = 2;
    scanf("%d", &n);

    while (i <= n) {
        sum += i;
        i += 2;
    }

    printf("%d", sum);
}
